  },
  {
    id: 4,
    image: Image,
    title: "Beginners's Guide to Marketing",
    instructor: "By Kwame Peprah",
    ratings: 1460,
    total_hours: 37,
    no_of_lectures: 178,
    level: "Beginner",
    price: 169.99,
  },
  
];

export default courses; // Default export
